    public class EventTable
extends javax.swing.JTable
    GUI_EventTable Class. Creates a table that holds all of the events for a sample. Each event also holds information regarding what type of injury occurred, which season it occurred during, the start year, and when an event finished recording.
    Author:
    Brendan Compton, Dylan Jones, and Alex Richter
    See Also:
